; Swimnerd Bluetooth Racing Clock - FinishLynx LSS Script
; Copyright (c) 2026 Swimnerd
;
; Hardware: STM32F103 + HC-08 Bluetooth + 6-digit LED display
; Protocol: Bluetooth Serial (SPP profile)
; Baud Rate: 9600,8,N,1
;
; Data Format: Simple ASCII time string
; Example: "01:23.45\n"
;
; The HC-08 Bluetooth module acts as a wireless serial port.
; FinishLynx sends to Bluetooth COM port → HC-08 → STM32 → Display

;;Initialization
; Sent once when FinishLynx connects
; Clear display and show ready state
\10\00CLR\0a

;;TimeRunning
; Sent while race clock is running
; Format: MM:SS.HH\n (newline terminated)
; Example: "01:23.45\n"
\11\01%s\0a

;;TimeStopped
; Sent when race clock stops
; Send final time
\11\01%s\0a

;;TimeUpdate
; Sent every second while running (optional - comment out if too frequent)
\11\01%s\0a

;;Result
; Sent when results are finalized
; Display winning time
\14\06%s\0a

;;Message
; Display custom message (e.g., "START" or "READY")
\16\01%s\0a
